
---

### How to Use:

1. Create a new repository on GitHub called `vpn-tmux-status-monitor`.
2. Clone the repository to your local machine.
3. Copy the directory structure and files (`vpn_status.sh`, `vpn-status.service`, `vpn-status.timer`, and `README.md`) to your local repository.
4. Push the changes to GitHub.

Let me know if you need any further assistance!
